  "content_id": "0ae87f62-dfd5-4ae5-acc2-28d3fae3f2fe",
  "description": "Register or renew registration with the Environment Agency to transport, buy, sell or broker waste.",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>You must register if your business does any of the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>transports waste (a carrier)</li>\n  <li>buys, sells or disposes of waste (a dealer)</li>\n  <li>arranges for someone else to buy, sell or dispose of waste (a broker)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can get an unlimited fine if you do not register.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There is a different process for registering as a waste carrier in <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.daera-ni.gov.uk/articles/registration-carriers-and-brokers\">Northern Ireland</a>, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.sepa.org.uk/regulations/waste/waste-carriers-and-brokers/\">Scotland</a> and <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://naturalresourceswales.gov.uk/permits-and-permissions/waste-permitting/register-as-a-waste-carrier-broker-or-dealer/?lang=en\">Wales</a>.</p>\n</div>\n",
    "more_information": "<p>Registration is usually free if you only transport waste you produce yourself. Otherwise, registration costs £154.</p>\n\n<p>If waste is your main business, you’ll need:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>names and dates of birth of the organisation’s executives, owners, directors or partners</li>\n  <li>details of any environmental offences they’ve committed</li>\n  <li>a way to pay (for example, a debit or credit card)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-happens-after-you-register\">What happens after you register</h3>\n\n<p>Once you’ve registered, your organisation’s details appear in the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://environment.data.gov.uk/public-register/view/search-waste-carriers-brokers\">public register of waste carriers, brokers and dealers</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"renew-your-registration\">Renew your registration</h3>\n\n<p>When you register, you’ll be told whether your registration is ‘upper tier’ or ‘lower tier’.</p>\n\n<p>If you have an upper tier registration, you must <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.wastecarriersregistration.service.gov.uk/\">renew your registration</a> every 3 years. It costs £105.</p>\n\n<p>You do not need to renew a lower tier registration.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-to-do-if-your-details-change\">What to do if your details change</h3>\n\n<p>You must contact the Environment Agency within 28 days to update your registration if:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>your organisation’s contact details change</li>\n  <li>your organisation’s management changes</li>\n  <li>someone in management is convicted of an environmental offence</li>\n  <li>your organisation changes what it does, for example you’re registered as a waste carrier but start acting as a waste broker as well</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>It costs £40 to change what your organisation does.</p>\n\n<p>You must make a new registration if:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>your business type has legally changed, for example if you change from a sole trader to a limited company</li>\n  <li>you’re changing from a lower tier to an upper tier registration</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>It costs £154 to make a new registration.</p>\n\n<p>Contact the Environment Agency if you’re not sure what to do.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"contact-the-environment-agency\">Contact the Environment Agency</h3>\n\n<p>Quote your registration number. You’ll find it on your registration letter or email - it starts with ‘CB’.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><a href=\"mailto:nccc-carrierbroker@environment-agency.gov.uk\">nccc-carrierbroker@environment-agency.gov.uk</a><br>\nTelephone: 03708 506 506<br>\nTelephone from outside the UK: +44 (0) 114 282 5312<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 6pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nEnvironment Agency general enquiries\n<br>National Customer Contact Centre\n<br>Quadrant 2\n<br>99 Parkway Avenue\n<br>Sheffield\n<br>S9 4WF\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
